   307→    <div class="badge">Validation Report — Refinement Cycle 6</div>
   308→    <h1>Vancouver Group Dinner<br><span style="color:#4ade80;">Cycle 6 Validation</span></h1>
   309→    <p>Two new findings this cycle: BC Spring Break ends on March 27 (not noted in any prior cycle), and Torafuku's group booking policy has been confirmed after being flagged as unresolved since Cycle 5.</p>
   310→    <div class="meta-row">
   311→      <div class="meta-chip">Friday March 27, 2026</div>
   312→      <div class="meta-chip">5–10 Guests, Greater Vancouver</div>
   313→      <div class="meta-chip">Viability Score: 91/100</div>
   314→      <div class="meta-chip-warn">Spring Break Ends March 27</div>
   315→      <div class="meta-chip-green">Torafuku Policy Confirmed</div>
   316→    </div>
